      <title>Cinven 搁置 10 亿英镑出售计划后寻求为 JLA 进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/cinven-seeks-refinancing-for-jla-after-shelving-1-billion-sale</link>
